#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:1 85ccce458f5d4739bf0f5ed78e1dd862
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:3 66ced06868b442ebb38a0ed0b5959ac0
msgid "What is InnoClaw?"
msgstr "什么是 InnoClaw？"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:5 9078981815fa4a5199dcce75e48697ce
msgid ""
"InnoClaw is an AI-powered research assistant web application similar to"
" Google NotebookLM. It lets you open server-side folders as "
"**workspaces**, browse and manage files, and chat with AI grounded in "
"your workspace files via **RAG** (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)."
msgstr ""
"InnoClaw 是一个类似于 Google NotebookLM 的 AI 驱动的研究助手 Web "
"应用程序。它允许您将服务器端文件夹作为**工作空间**打开，浏览和管理文件，并通过 **RAG**（检索增强生成）与基于工作空间文件的 AI "
"进行对话。"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:7 6d90ba0d5943423b83c5547985e49126
msgid "Key Features"
msgstr "核心功能"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:9 c38049e4804a4a67a3a35cad0083581d
msgid "**Workspace Management** — Map server folders as persistent workspaces"
msgstr "**工作空间管理** —— 将服务器文件夹映射为持久化工作空间"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:10 b7530b2c85e547e8b23f3bebcb571f00
msgid "**File Browser** — Tree view with upload, create, edit, rename, and delete"
msgstr "**文件浏览器** —— 树形视图，支持上传、创建、编辑、重命名和删除"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:11 ea85798a03f94e77b153787b2ad5dda2
msgid ""
"**GitHub Integration** — Clone and pull GitHub repositories (including "
"private ones)"
msgstr "**GitHub 集成** —— 克隆和拉取 GitHub 仓库（包括私有仓库）"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:12 41fb30c8e4cd43ddb31005588de2357e
msgid ""
"**RAG Chat** — AI answers questions based on workspace file content with "
"source citations"
msgstr "**RAG 对话** —— AI 基于工作空间文件内容回答问题，并附带来源引用"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:13 240631d41a6b4e2681b0fcbaab55b4cb
msgid "**Note Generation** — Auto-generate summaries, FAQs, briefs, and timelines"
msgstr "**笔记生成** —— 自动生成摘要、常见问题、简报和时间线"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:14 0e9964022bf24937a68391a185ca398a
msgid "**Multi-LLM Support** — Switch between OpenAI GPT and Anthropic Claude"
msgstr "**多 LLM 支持** —— 在 OpenAI GPT 和 Anthropic Claude 之间切换"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:15 350697090e1e48989db28256a763f2b4
msgid "**Bilingual UI** — Chinese / English toggle"
msgstr "**双语界面** —— 中文 / 英文切换"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:16 d62e9f6331ed4962be26ddd4572f5b36
msgid "**Dark Mode** — Light and dark theme support"
msgstr "**暗色模式** —— 支持浅色和深色主题"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:17 ac8dd06e52474a54a4b1f3b77d679622
msgid "**Bot Integrations** — Feishu (Lark) and WeChat Enterprise bot support"
msgstr "**机器人集成** —— 支持飞书和企业微信机器人"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:18 8a7581d0ab224312b6cd29b393c24da8
msgid ""
"**Agent Mode** — Autonomous AI agent with tool usage (bash, file "
"operations, kubectl)"
msgstr "**Agent 模式** —— 具备工具调用能力的自主 AI 代理（bash、文件操作、kubectl）"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:19 0c09e6288c2d4c7e8ed48c5513e53ea3
msgid "**Skills** — Reusable prompt templates for common tasks"
msgstr "**技能** —— 用于常见任务的可复用提示词模板"

