#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:76 ee428acab1e84f84b75e828f2d2dd15c
msgid "RAG Pipeline"
msgstr "RAG 流水线"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:78 9fa7c3c5aaae4fc2b77bcbd759a67916
msgid ""
"The core feature of InnoClaw is RAG-based AI chat. The pipeline works "
"in three stages:"
msgstr "InnoClaw 的核心功能是基于 RAG 的 AI 对话。流水线分为三个阶段："

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:103 b85eac1ba9af438fb46c321400d49476
msgid ""
"**Indexing** — When the user clicks \"Sync\", files are scanned, text is "
"extracted, chunked, and embedded into vectors stored in SQLite."
msgstr "**索引** —— 当用户点击\"同步\"时，扫描文件，提取文本，分块，并将向量嵌入存储到 SQLite 中。"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:104 0b72a2dd8be24ec4af0c2b088e4def62
msgid ""
"**Retrieval** — When the user asks a question, the question is embedded "
"and compared against all stored vectors using cosine similarity to find "
"the top 8 most relevant chunks."
msgstr "**检索** —— 当用户提问时，将问题向量化，并使用余弦相似度与所有存储的向量进行比较，找到最相关的前 8 个文本块。"

#: ../../getting-started/overview.md:105 d5a324c3d5014ff0a620155036821976
msgid ""
"**Generation** — The relevant chunks and the user's question are sent to "
"the LLM, which generates a streaming answer with source citations."
msgstr "**生成** —— 将相关文本块和用户的问题发送给 LLM，生成带有来源引用的流式回答。"
